{
  "stem": "4963.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember standing with my Uncle Osher and with the whole family right there with the children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my uncle somehow found out right away which was, was death and which one was life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we were alerted right away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we made sure that we were separated, you know, into life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so-- however, they did-- the Germans did, you know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] separate us into the, you know, right side, where I suppose we was life.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then after, oh, about-- this went on for, I think, a whole day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after that day, we were told that we could go back to our houses and that the other people were just going to be evacuated to another city for work.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was-- I think it was, like-- it was the big Aktion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think it took place in October of 1941-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so October or November.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I told you, I'm not very good in dates.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because one of the reasons of my survival, as I mentioned to you, was to block out things as I went along.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I didn't want to really remember bad things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I just moved on and said, OK, it's-- let's see what, what comes ahead of me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So then later on that night, we started hearing gunshots.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the next day or a couple days later, some people who were thrown into the graves, into to the holes, really-- they just-- they lined them up-- told us what had happened.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were given up as dead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They just lined up all these people, 10,000 people around a, a hole.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were machine guns.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They just shot them all.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
